    "description": "<strong>《粘性高尔夫》</strong> 是一款3D竞速平台跳跃游戏，游戏中的物体可以粘在你的高尔夫球上。击出高尔夫球，让它穿越各种赛道，收集越来越多的物体，并争取一杆进洞！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >维持动能</h2>从一个助推器跃至另一个助推器，确保一杆抵达每关终点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1338c1d6e3c5ad996a46a0629c023274.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >粘住万物</h2>路障、树木、房屋……提高你的质量来收集更大的物体。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/1f2c9aa1a363dd757435e39fe32cd85e.mp4?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控赛道</h2>检验你的聪明才智和技巧，完成额外目标并攀登排行榜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/69231c0dece3bb4763ed8466703fb1a8.poster.avif?t=1708794120\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299080/extras/69231c0dece3bb4763ed8466703fb1a8.webm?t=1708794120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/